name: Craft
tagline: " Craft " is a web programming language powered by PHP.
body:
### Welcome to Craft!
Craft is a web programming language which is powered by PHP and it's currently under development.

### Craft Server
To install Craft server, simply download the Craft installer to your linux server then run it. For more information(s) please refer to our wiki.

### Authors and Contributors
@protldnetwork - Main Developer.

### Support or Contact
If you want to contact us, or if you're asking for support -> [documentation](https://protldnetwork.github.io/craft/docs) or [contact support](mailto:admin@protld.host)
